{"tid":1418101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有計]唔想打死人又唔想放人走","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:51:00.000Z","uid":102535,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47db4d39de839f52ba2a708c9f9e94d04f31fc1f","tid":1418101,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:50:42.000Z","msg":"明白和理非唔想見血<br />\n但有啲人唔比啲代價佢只會變本加厲<br />\n但講真<br />\n黑社會個啲比人打一身對佢地嚟講只係家常便飯<br />\n依個時候就要諗諗計去懲罰佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCrCNg3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCrCNg3.png&h=713fe542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n材料包括但不限於：<br />\n一碌燈柱<br />\n一條人棍<br />\n索帶用嚟綁手腳，再綁係燈柱<br />\n保鮮紙紮粽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非今次無潔癖啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"613ede9c689fb44129b5030ce4342bd3c064fdca","tid":1418101,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求，缺一不可</code>"},{"pid":"e8e4290c07b25264dbf6358c449c1a8158b32ce9","tid":1418101,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求，缺一不可</code>"},{"pid":"3f138b126bfe7ecca68074299634976ea291d390","tid":1418101,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求，缺一不可</code>"},{"pid":"7dd40aeee46f978fd7ee30f9dd3f276afe9a312c","tid":1418101,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求，缺一不可</code>"},{"pid":"fcb8f316bf074c3bd6104fc31ccfee23101efad1","tid":1418101,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:52:47.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求，缺一不可</code>"},{"pid":"6d8b9f5352465ed1a023d93543c4efd2de904654","tid":1418101,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,